remarks.para:
For example, if the integer array is equal to { 1, 2, 4, 8, 16 } and the range is set
            to [0, 1], then the histogram consists of next subranges:


[0.0, 0.2] - 1 hit;

[0.2, 0.4] - 2 hits;

[0.4, 0.6] - 4 hits;

[0.6, 0.8] - 8 hits;

[0.8, 1.0] - 16 hits.

